name: Disney by Loungefly Wallet Sleeping Beauty Lenticular Princess Series Wristlet
description:
Dream up enchanting adventures with our Loungefly Disney Sleeping Beauty Princess Lenticular Wristlet Wallet. On the front, applique woodland creatures, dressed up as a royal prince, look into a window view of Aurora with Prince Phillip. In an alternate lenticular view, Aurora's with the woodland creatures, telling them all about her dream prince. Debossed flowers and more woodland creatures frame the window of this pink wallet, and on the back, a squirrel and a rabbit make an encore appearance, surrounded by flowers. Inside, you'll find 8 slots for holding cards and 1 clear slot for displaying your ID. An interior zipper pocket allows for extra room in this larger-sized wristlet wallet. A die-cut shape of a flower, on the clear ID slot, adds a charming touch. Make a dreamy entrance wherever you go with this stylish vision of a wallet. The Loungefly Disney Sleeping Beauty Princess Lenticular Wristlet Wallet is made of vegan leather (polyurethane). Wallet zips closed with shiny gold-colored metal hardware. Additional features include applique, debossed, lenticular, and printed details. Take note of the coordinating inside lining. This wallet is an officially licensed Disney product. Wallet dimensions: 8"W x 4"H

- Material: 100% PU Leather
- Size: 20 x 2,5 x 10 cm
